Our Prime Objective and Goal is focused towards making Andhra Pradesh, as the Worlds Happiest State to achieve this.And it is one of the key independent variable\n
of World Happiness Index report 2016 is healthy life expectancy at birth Out of the 6 Independent Variables , HealthCare parameter contributes to one of the highest happiness index.While couple of private service providers are working on digitalisation of healthcare services in Urban areas, theres immense necessity of developing a tool which caters to Rural people in native language.( Rural population contributes to 63% (approx.) of your current population). Our Goal is to provide Healthcare solution to Rural population where a FARMER sitting at his hometown should be able to book appoints (for doctor, diagnostic) at a single click along with Hospital information , Blood bank information, Medical shops delivering medicines at your door step, AMBULANCE services 24/7 from any where in the state of Andhra Pradesh.As Andhra Pradesh is the first state heading towards FIBER GRID-CONNECTING TO THE LAST MILE this tool should every single User ( patient ,doctor, diagnostics , medical stores, hospitals,ambulance services and so on ) to easily connect with each other THROUGH OUR WEB SITE, MOBILE APP and SAVE LIFES.\n
Connecting a common man from Rural Area to get the BEST Health Care Services at their DOOR STEP and ON THE GO at a CLICK.\n
Create a revolutionary solution which will transform HEALTH CARE.\n
